<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> Before granting any allowance, the appointing authority shall see whether the accomodation is suitable for the requirements of the official, having regard to his duties and his family circumstances, and the number of dependants actually living under his roof. </inglise>
